author: etnu
msg: Added support for Link elements, facilitating lifecycle events and link metadata, as required by SHINDIG-341.
This just adds the elements to ModulePrefs and the metadata output handler. It does not perform any actions on lifecycle events at the moment, such as pinging the url end points.
It's not clear if the task of hitting the end points is the job of Shindig or not.
